Finance-Bank-IE-PermanentTSB version 0.01
=========================================

This is an interface to Permanent TSB Ireland homebanking

Finance::Bank::IE::PermanentTSB supports only check_balance at the
moment.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    WWW::Mechanize
    HTML::TokeParser::Simple
    Date::Calc

